<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>TENDERLY PLEADING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kiheiin mimang lungkham leh gimthei,
 Ngaiin, Belampu pha'n tu'n A hun sam;
 Hukdam ding leh silthien di'n A hun ngak,
 Kinin, Amah pawm di'n vaigei ta ki'n.

[V2]
 Aw nemin A hun sam, A hun chiel zing,
 Belampu pha hun sapna ngaiin;
 Aw nemin A hun sam, A hun chiel zing,
 Lungsiet awn &quot;Ei hun zuonun&quot; A tii.

[V3]
 2. A hun ngak zing hi, bang dia mangthai ding?
 Huong apat vakmang gamla mahleh chin;
 A hinna thisan in A hun tan tai,
 A hehpih mak gen theih ding guol ei puoi!

[V4]
 3. A thu ngaiin, A lungsiet ngaihtuoh in,
 Gilo kimahleh nang gitloh A puo'i;
 Ngaihdamna bukim leh kumsawt hinna,
 A tatna zalin nang a hun pie tai.

[V5]
 4. Lamlui ah hungin lam dik ah hungin,
 Isu achun lutin, Kawtkhak ahi;
 Belampu ahi, Aw nemin hun sam,
 Hatlo sa'n hung inla, vakvai ta ki'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>241</hymn_number>
</song>